        public static void playSound(org.bukkit.entity.Player origin,
                             org.bukkit.Sound sound,
                             float baseVolume,
                             float pitch,
                             float maxDistance)
        Plays the sound to all players within the given distance originating from the player origin. The further away from the origin the surrounding players are, the quieter it will take.
        Parameters:
        origin - The player the sound originates from
        sound - The sound to play
        pitch - The pitch of the sound
        maxDistance - The maximum distance away the sound will be played to other players
